Title: Rucinni High Fashion Gold Alloy Tennis Bracelet & Licenced Swarovski Crystals
Description: All Our Items are gift boxed High Fashion Rucinni Tennis Bracelet with Swarovski Crystal elements pave set in gold alloy, which is guaranteed for it's lifetime not to tarnish or flake off. The bracelet is 7.5 inches = 19cms in length and closes by means of a secure box clasp. The Sparkling crystals are very secure each in their own cradle and the bracelet is very flexible. Weight 42.2 grams SHIPPING WITHIN AUSTRALIA We ship via Tracked Delivery Service for all jewellery. INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING Pack and Track via Australia Post and their affiliates. Items are registered and insured. We cannot mark items as gifts so do please check your items suitability with your county's customs service.
